ItemDesc: A mature heliobus that ran away after the Flaming Catastrophe War. Used to level up Traces moderately for <color=#f29e38ff>Nihility</color> characters.
ItemBGDesc: A mean and nasty heliobus that appears like a full flame. The size of a heliobus's flame when it materializes indicates its strength. This torch-like heliobus has just tasted consciousness and is eager to devour its host's emotions and desires. "Absorb their emotions and sway their wills..."
